{"tid":2368512,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"驚喜！BLACKPINK Jennie 開個人 YouTube 頻道　送上自製翻唱 MV","createTime":"2021-01-16T09:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T12:28:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3e8314a358394a8b5a4cdbddee8c5c4f8f6b3736","tid":2368512,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"Jennie 選在自己的生日這天為大家送上了禮物，以後除了追蹤她的 Instagram 外，也能隨時期待她更新 YouTube 頻道啦！Blinks 都訂閱了嗎？<br />\n<br />\nJennie 在今天（16 日）上午公開了自己的 YouTube 頻道，用了和 Instagram 帳號一樣的名字 &ldquo;Jennierubyjane&rdquo;，並上傳了第一支向全世界問好的影片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在這支短短四分多鐘的影片中，Jennie 透露自己一直在想該在生日時做什麼，最後決定錄自己的日常生活來跟大家分享。就像生活風格類的 YouTuber，Jennie 緊接著介紹了自己的穿搭，還試著說「請大家記得按讚，訂⋯⋯」結果忍不住笑場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=erYPvNbc_mc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DerYPvNbc_mc&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyMFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=f8e564cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=erYPvNbc_mc</a><br />\n<br />\n在後半段的影片中，Jennie 翻唱 Mandy Moore 的 &ldquo;When Will My Life Being?&rdquo;，巧妙地配合歌詞內容，以日常影片做成自製 MV，展現與平時截然不同的搞笑魅力。<br />\n<br />\n在結束影片前，Jennie 也說：「希望大家喜歡我今天準備的影片，我以後也會努力製作更好的影片。我也要謝謝所有祝我生日快樂的 Blinks，我相信我一定會度過一場最棒的生日。等不及見到你們了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_10f13e6e84fa641dddd654ae62178d23/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-16/133057-893647.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_10f13e6e84fa641dddd654ae62178d23%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-16%2F133057-893647.jpg&h=bd8a54a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_896f9b210b2028ced13b0bdadaa74558/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-16/133057-893645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_896f9b210b2028ced13b0bdadaa74558%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-16%2F133057-893645.jpg&h=8e5d3f88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9d331522e17ff8125bdf2421079376d8de7cb5b","tid":2368512,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3609bc2a05a6ac21a757732fb222b98609fc16aa","tid":2368512,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:20:20.000Z","msg":"支持...！"},{"pid":"80a44430e98fb1b392e0bea2320d80f02c7181b3","tid":2368512,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"我地Jennie多才多藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85d22092bc8298b3ea962a509d01cc7518a2b97","tid":2368512,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80a44430e98fb1b392e0bea2320d80f02c7181b3","tid":2368512,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"我地Jennie多才多藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:43:39.000Z","msg":"太屈了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d43a6ed5e95583cef187e14533b7c7d1af8943","tid":2368512,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d85d22092bc8298b3ea962a509d01cc7518a2b97","tid":2368512,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80a44430e98fb1b392e0bea2320d80f02c7181b3","tid":2368512,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"我地Jennie多才多藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:43:39.000Z","msg":"太屈了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"